richtext.name: n1
richtext.text: In the base game, when 3 appear on the reels, the free game function can be triggered and 6 free spins are obtained. In the base game, when 4 appear on the reels, the free game function can be triggered and 9 free spins are obtained. In the base game, when 5 appear on the reels, the free game function can be triggered and 12 free spins are obtained. In a free game, when appears on the reels, the number of free games can be increased by 1.
